Filelist
========
array.txt
  Bash Arrays

basename.txt
  Get basename of file
  ls | sed 's/\(.*\)\..*/\1/'
    or
  BASENAME=${1%\.*}
    Where $1 is the filename to get basename from.
    or
  basename - strip directory and suffix from filenames

